import React from 'react'
import { Button, Form, Message } from 'semantic-ui-react'

const FormSuccess = () => (
  <Form success>
    <Form.Input label='Title' placeholder='Kind of Blue' />
    <Form.Input label='Artist' placeholder='Miles Davis' />
    <Form.Input label='Genre' placeholder='Jazz' />
    <Form.Input label='Vendor' placeholder='Waterloo Records' />
    <Form.Input label='Condition' placeholder='joe@schmoe.com' />
    <Form.Input label='Cost' placeholder='joe@schmoe.com' />
    <Form.Input label='Purchased' placeholder='joe@schmoe.com' />
    <Form.Input label='Released' placeholder='joe@schmoe.com' />
    <Form.Input label='Cover URL' placeholder='joe@schmoe.com' />

    <Message
      success
      header='Form Completed'
      content="Album Successfully Added!"
    />
    <Button>Submit</Button>
  </Form>
)

export default FormSuccess
